For years, I didn't write
about my hike on the PCT

00:21:31.520 --> 00:21:33.620
because I had nothing to
say really about it.

00:21:33.620 --> 00:21:35.650
If I met you, we could talk
about it and it would be a

00:21:35.650 --> 00:21:36.970
nice conversation.

00:21:36.970 --> 00:21:41.920
But until I really had something
to say in the realm

00:21:41.920 --> 00:21:46.510
of art which is, I think,
